{"_id":"5HHqKmz2N7n2zU0s","name":"Critical Miss","img":"modules/gurps-instant-defaults/img/icons/miss.png","description":"","results":[{"_id":"rH26cxM6qEPPK2sl","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Critical Miss</b> <br />Your weapon breaks. If it is <i>Fine, Very Fine, magical,</i> a <i>firearm</i>, or a <i>solid crushing weapon</i>, roll again. <br />If you roll this result a second time, the weapon breaks; if not, you drop it instead.","img":"worlds/viking/adventures/Adventure_1620643926068/table/table/Fa0Xywc4KJ1hc01l/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,4],"drawn":false,"rangeL":3,"rangeH":4,"collection":null,"resultId":null},{"_id":"72jcnviv6FR4BcUv","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Critical Miss</b> <br />You hit yourself in the <b>Arm</b> or <b>Leg</b>. If this is an <i>impaling</i>, <i>piercing</i>, or <i>ranged</i> attack, roll again. <br />If you roll this result a second time, you hit yourself; if not, use the second result.","img":"worlds/viking/adventures/Adventure_1620643926068/table/table/Fa0Xywc4KJ1hc01l/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"rangeL":5,"rangeH":5,"collection":null,"resultId":null},{"_id":"T1zCZHE5RXJeFTKo","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Critical Miss</b> <br />You hit yourself in the <b>Arm</b> or <b>Leg</b> for half damage. If this is an <i>impaling</i>, <i>piercing</i>, or <i>ranged</i> attack, roll again. <br />If you roll this result a second time, you hit yourself; if not, use the second result.","img":"worlds/viking/adventures/Adventure_1620643926068/table/table/Fa0Xywc4KJ1hc01l/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"rangeL":6,"rangeH":6,"collection":null,"resultId":null},{"_id":"dZTOL34KHXqyxxNr","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Critical Miss</b> <br />You lose your balance and can do <i>nothing else</i> until your next turn (not even free actions). All <i>Active Defenses</i> are at <b>-2</b> until then.","img":"worlds/viking/adventures/Adventure_1620643926068/table/table/Fa0Xywc4KJ1hc01l/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"rangeL":7,"rangeH":7,"collection":null,"resultId":null},{"_id":"7mcuX7Fa0BP3Jhiz","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Critical Miss</b> <br />The weapon unreadies; you must take a <b>Ready</b> maneuver before you can use it again.","img":"worlds/viking/adventures/Adventure_1620643926068/table/table/Fa0Xywc4KJ1hc01l/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"rangeL":8,"rangeH":8,"collection":null,"resultId":null},{"_id":"rUQ0TYfuSGDIXJBX","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Critical Miss</b> <br />You drop your weapon. A cheap weapon breaks (p. 485).","img":"worlds/viking/adventures/Adventure_1620643926068/table/table/Fa0Xywc4KJ1hc01l/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[9,11],"drawn":false,"rangeL":9,"rangeH":11,"collection":null,"resultId":null},{"_id":"7tsE7iJZ2D8tymON","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Critical Miss</b> <br />The weapon unreadies; you must take a <b>Ready</b> maneuver before you can use it again.","img":"worlds/viking/adventures/Adventure_1620643926068/table/table/Fa0Xywc4KJ1hc01l/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"rangeL":12,"rangeH":12,"collection":null,"resultId":null},{"_id":"NruERhfvT856BMbf","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Critical Miss</b> <br />You lose your balance and can do <i>nothing else</i> until your next turn (not even free actions). All <i>Active Defenses</i> are at <b>-2</b> until then.","img":"worlds/viking/adventures/Adventure_1620643926068/table/table/Fa0Xywc4KJ1hc01l/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false,"rangeL":13,"rangeH":13,"collection":null,"resultId":null},{"_id":"294CAptjk2YhNAmK","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Critical Miss</b> <br /> <b>* Swinging Melee Attack</b> <br />Your weapon flies [[1d6]] yards from you (50% chance forward or backward). Anyone in the weapon's landing hex must roll vs. DX to avoid taking half damage from the weapon. <br /><br /><b>* All Other Cases</b> <br />You drop the weapon. A cheap weapon breaks (p. 485).","img":"